name: OLD BITCH IN HELL
description:
I got pissed off by this old whore with her stupid braid.

She pinned into my Hell those people who don't fit into the portrait 
of my preferred audience.


Brief statistics for the week:

- 33 people who sipped tea loudly during their lifetime;
- 1987 pseudo-vegans;
- 901 people who love to bite their nails;
- 45 people who like to argue for no reason;
- 771 Gamers in Battle Royale

Where are the people really deserving of Hell, old bitch?


I had no choice but to kill Death, return home, sit on the windowsill, 
look out the window and masturbate in tears
as I slowly sip on tomato juice (I hope it was him)


Routine.




:: visuals: @cryptohamster | sound-design: @dontbesovasya
